reviews.text:
I mixed up a couple smaller batches of this recipe, one of them being what's written here, and one with an added INW Plum at 0.25%.&#xD;
The original simple tobacco is delicious! It's a rich tobacco with a tasty aromatic feeling to it. I'm all about the aromatics, so in my 2am dazed fog, I thought that INW plum would fit the bill perfectly. It turned out better than I expected in all honesty. Plum mostly added a slightly darker note to the mix along with a touch of tart.&#xD;
&#xD;
For a tobacco base, this recipe is superb on it's own, or something you can easily add a couple other flavors to in order to give you own touch to it. Thank you for this recipe Fear!
